text: Humperdinck or Humperdink is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Engelbert Humperdinck (composer) (1854–1921), German composer * Engelbert Humperdinck (singer) (born 1936), English pop singer * Oliver Humperdink (born John Jay Sutton) (1949–2011), American professional wrestling manager * Prince Humperdinck, a character from the 1973 novel The Princess Bride and the 1987 film adaptation of the same name ==See also== * Humperdink Duck, a Disney character, grandfather of Donald Duck
title: Humperdinck
